Package org.livingdoc.repositories.confluence

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConfluenceRepository
    This implementation of a DocumentRepository uses a Confluence server to get the Documents from. The remote Confluence server can be configured in the livingdoc.yml config section of the repository.
    ConfluenceRepositoryConfig
    The configuration object for the Confluence Repository.
    ConfluenceRepositoryFactory
    This Factory is used to create a ConfluenceRepository. This Factory must be specified in the livingdoc.yml to use the Confluence Repository. For more details about the {@see ConfluenceRepository} see it's documentation.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ConfluenceDocumentNotFoundException
